</dd></dl><p><b>CERTTRANSDBCOLUMN Structures (variable):</b> An
array of <b>CERTTRANSDBCOLUMN</b> structures. These structures MUST be
contiguous and MUST NOT be padded. All structures MUST appear prior to any
information about the column <span><a href="c6451297-197d-4b4b-b786-3f3187b67b8f#gt_fd49ea36-576c-4417-93bd-d1ac63e71093" data-linktype="relative-path">schema</a></span> data, which
appears in the <b>Column_Schema_Data</b> byte array at the end of the packet.</p><dl>
<dd>
